sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as 用户
    participant C as Client
    participant A as Auth
    participant API as API
    participant DB as DB

    U->>C: 登录
    C->>A: 凭证
    A-->>C: access + refresh
    Note over C,A: 不落盘 refresh 明文
    C->>API: 请求 + Bearer
    API->>A: 校验 token
    A-->>API: OK / claims
    API->>DB: 读资源
    DB-->>API: rows
    API-->>C: 200 JSON
    C-->>U: 渲染

